        </tbody>
    </table>
</section>

<section class="cgu-section">
    <h2>4. The free tier (Basic)</h2>
    <p>
        Every account receives <strong>1,000 free tokens</strong>, automatically
        <strong>renewed every 8 hours</strong>. The counter starts on your first activity after
        account creation. Free tokens do not accumulate: at each renewal, the free balance is
        reset to 1,000.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="cgu-section">
    <h2>5. Prepaid packs</h2>
    <p>Need more? You can buy <strong>stackable</strong> packs:</p>
    <table class="cgu-table">
        <thead><tr><th>Pack</th><th>Price</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td>Intermediate — 10,000 tokens</td><td>$10</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Professional — 50,000 tokens</td><td>$40</td></tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>
        Prepaid tokens are consumed first; once depleted, you automatically fall back to the
        free tier (1,000 tokens / 8 h).
    </p>
</section>

<section class="cgu-section">
    <h2>6. What happens when tokens run out?</h2>
    <p>
        When your balance (free + prepaid) is no longer enough, <strong>reading and writing are
        temporarily blocked</strong>. You can then either <strong>top up</strong> a pack or
        <strong>wait for the next renewal</strong> of your free allowance (within 8 hours).
    </p>
</section>

<section class="cgu-section">
    <h2>7. Who pays and who consumes?</h2>
    <p>
        The <strong>company owner</strong> pays. Any activity performed within a company — by its
        owner <em>or</em> by invited collaborators — is deducted from that company owner's balance.
    </p>
</section>
